@node "Features" "Features..."
  
 @{b}The features...@{ub}
 
 + fast scan algorythm for highest performance
 - defineable colors
 - optional header display
 + overview of total uploads/fakes in files/bytes
 - All files optional sortable
 - changing filenames to upper/lowercase
 - en/disabling of the dateline
 - user defineable number of files per line
 + and even some more fine options

 @{b}All options marked with '-' are only for registered Users!
 @{ub}
 @{b}@{u}NOTE:@{ub}@{uu} Some features are disabled in the public version
@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation..."
 
 @{b}Installation...@{ub}
 
 Just double-click the install icon of your preferred language and follow the
 installer.
 
 I spend a lot of time to write the installer script, so I won`t explain how
 to install dre!new manual.
@endnode

