   No warranties are given. I take no responsibility of any possible
   harm this product could do to your amiga system (not that it would but..).

 * You may NOT sell this product without permission from me.

 * Program must not be altered in any way.

 * Package must always be kept intact when spreading.

 * It is OK to include this on CD-ROM & disk collections and distribute
   it through aminet and other such ftp's and file nets.

 Above mentioned rules apply to dRE!WEEk and other texts/libraries
 within the original package versions 2.0 and newer unless otherwise stated.
@endnode

@node "Registerware" "Registerware"
 
 All tools I've made in the past are released under the @{b}RegisterWare@{ub} concept.
 This means, that I release all my doors only one time as full working Public
 Versions, all updates/bugfixings are only available for registered Users.

 The Registration costs @{b}30.- DM@{ub} (or $20) and has to be paid only @{b}*ONE*@{ub}
 time for @{b}*ALL*@{ub} BBS-doors I have made until now. Of course all new 
 doors are included in this registration fee, too.

 To become registered user, contact one of the following Boards and leave a
 mail to dR.dRE!/tRSi about Registration:

 @{b}pUNISHMENT iNC:@{ub} +49(0) 30 694 8470 (v.34) - fAME tEST/sUPPORT BBS!
                 +49(0) 30 694 8570 (v.34)

 @{b}Paralysis:@{ub}      +49(0) 30 721 6071 (v.34)
                 +49(0) 30 721 6072 (v.34)
                 +49(0) 30 721 6073 (v.34)
                 +49(0) 30 721 6065 (v.34)

 @{b}Devils Point:@{ub} Absolute Private

              @{fg shine}These Boards are supporting only 100% Public Domain.@{fg text}

                 You could also use E-Mail to contact me:

                    @{b}E-Mail:@{ub} dr.dre@mail.niederrhein.de

       Or simply send the register fee, an envelope with stamps and 
               a formatted disk to my postal address below:

                         @{fg fill}      Bodo Hoffmann
                              Kapitelstraße 1
                                41460 Neuss
                                  Germany@{fg text}
@endnode

